{"tid":2432033,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"facebook呢招封鎖遲早用落香港度","createTime":"2021-03-04T04:50:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T06:51:21.000Z","uid":113951,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d12d57bad276c0f10cf84f3a097c6860255b626c","tid":2432033,"uid":113951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T04:50:30.000Z","msg":"黨安法依法封鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//土耳其的電訊管理部門(BTK)早已「提醒」FB，要小心處理戰爭傷者的相片，並強調如果有專頁變成分享這些「非法」內容的中心點，當局就可能會要求封鎖專頁。<br />\n<br />\n  而FB內部，則建議以「地緣封鎖」(Geo-blocking)的方法應對。「地緣封鎖」即是根據用戶的網絡地區，去決定是否顯示某個專頁或內容。換言之，FB打算只禁止土耳其境內的用戶閱讀YPG專頁。<br />\n<br />\n  對此Bickert負責的內容審查部門，向管理層分析了「地緣封鎖」的後果：這會令土耳其外各方的社運人士的注意到這個封鎖行動，以及引起未來對地緣封鎖方法的關注。//<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://mewe.com/p/blackmirrortech/show/60401bf8da97cc6a754bdee8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fp%2Fblackmirrortech%2Fshow%2F60401bf8da97cc6a754bdee8&d=Xhragic3nybqeCAZBODyv6GvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=c11cb0c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/p/blackmirrortech/show/60401bf8da97cc6a754bdee8</a>"},{"pid":"8d8459df6e73640aeb3916ddd411ee19ab25cd48","tid":2432033,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T04:52:22.000Z","msg":"一block就要block晒支那區"},{"pid":"d69ec3a2a8c0425175a9ceff9384f320b4b001c2","tid":2432033,"uid":113951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d8459df6e73640aeb3916ddd411ee19ab25cd48","tid":2432033,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T04:52:22.000Z","msg":"一block就要block晒支那區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T05:49:52.000Z","msg":"要比入支那先有得block喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae4a7d34d93a3ed94f5b4c387a800e419b29ce2","tid":2432033,"uid":55568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d69ec3a2a8c0425175a9ceff9384f320b4b001c2","tid":2432033,"uid":113951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8